snippet.title: Osminog Adventures - Update 0.9: The Story Concluded
snippet.description:
Short Teaser for the upcoming Update to the RPG Maker 2k Project "Osminog Adventures - The Lost Island".

Wanna get the game and not miss an Update? Hop onto the Discord:
https://discord.gg/gmpBVVnQ

Or visit me on twitch to join the Development Process:
www.twitch.tv/nahro1001


Teaser Music Provided by the awesome Untold Journey:
